long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
可以帮助您防止无意中打开会让人上瘾的网站。您可以轻松地添加，删除，和开启需要屏蔽的网站，再也不必担心意外地进入这些容易沉迷的网站。此外，它还将给您一次重新思考您将要做什么的机会，从而提高您的生产力，保持集中精力。

It can help prevent you from unintentionally opening an addictive website. You can easily add, remove, and open sites that need to be blocked without having to worry about accidentally accessing those easily addicted sites. In addition, it will give you a chance to rethink what you are going to do to increase your productivity and stay focused.
